  { q: "How do I get my first direct booking?", a: "Start with past guests. After checkout, send a thank-you email with a link to your direct booking site and a discount code for their next stay. This is the fastest path to direct bookings because these guests already know and trust your property. Referrals from happy guests are your second-best source." },
  { q: "Should I stop using Airbnb once I have a direct booking site?", a: "No. The best strategy is using both. Airbnb is a powerful discovery engine for new guests. Once guests have a great stay, redirect them to your direct site for repeat bookings. Think of Airbnb as your marketing channel and your direct site as your retention channel." }
